#19600
The Titan's Maw~
   You stand before the gaping maw of a fallen titan, its fossilized 
jaw unhinged and fused to the cavern floor. Massive teeth jut from 
the ground like jagged pillars of white stone. The air here is 
stagnant and heavy with the scent of ancient dust and ozone. Deep 
within the throat of the beast, you hear the skittering of claws 
against bone. Bioluminescent crystals cling to the soft tissue 
remnants lining the throat, casting a sickly violet glow that 
illuminates the shadows where scavengers lurk.
~
