#19602
The Spine Corridor~
   This narrow path runs directly along the length of the titan's massive 
spinal column. On either side, the vertebrae rise like jagged cliffs, 
narrowing the walkway to a treacherous ledge. Below, you can see into the 
abyssal depths of the cavern floor, far below where the crystals grow 
thickest. The wind howls through the hollow holes in the spine, creating a 
haunting, flute-like melody that is disorienting to the unprepared. Sharp 
shards of crystal jut from the walls at irregular angles, resembling the 
teeth of a trap. You notice deep gouges in the bone floor - scars left by 
weapons far too large to belong to anything mortal.
~
