#19603
The Ossuary Pit~
    The corridor opens abruptly into a vast, vertical shaft that
plunges deep into the earth. This is the titan's discarded waste -
a chasm filled with shattered bone fragments and piles of calcified
debris falling away into total darkness. Wind whips up from the
depths, carrying shards of sharp crystal that sting your skin. The
floor here is treacherous; loose vertebrae shift underfoot, threatening
to send you sliding over the edge. Scavengers nest on the precarious
ledges overlooking the abyss, their crystal-encrusted shells blending
perfectly with the jagged surroundings.
~
