#19604
Skull Sanctum~
   You have breached the cranial cavity of the titan. The walls here
are smooth and curved, resembling the inside of a massive skull.
Two hollow sockets gaze out into the darkness, lined with jagged
teeth that once served as filters for magical radiation. The air
hums with raw arcane energy. Massive geodes have grown from the
'brain matter' residue on the floor, pulsing with a rhythmic violet
light that threatens to overload your senses. This was clearly a
place of power for the entity in life; now it is a dangerous trap
for those who seek to plunder its remains.
~
