#19605
The Crystal Hive~
   This chamber has been completely overtaken by a dense forest of
jagged, violet crystals. They grow so thickly that there is barely
room to walk without risking impalement. The ground is uneven and 
slick with a translucent slime secreted by the massive growths. 
You are not alone here. Dozens of Scavengers - massive arachnids
with carapaces fused from shards of these very crystals - skitter 
across the ceiling and walls, watching you with multifaceted eyes. 
The air is thick with the sound of chittering claws and the low 
thrum of crystal magic.
~
