#19614
The Aorta Chamber~
   You step into a massive circular chamber where a great artery once
pulsed with life. The walls are lined with thick, petrified tubes of 
bone and crystal that radiate intense heat. This is the final barrier
before the core itself. The scavengers here are larger, their 
carapaces thick enough to deflect blows from seasoned adventurers. A 
low hum vibrates through the floor, signaling the proximity of the 
titan's heart.
